name: Morning Hike and Fishing along Rich and  Rough and Tumble Creeks
Afternoon Run - persistent cold/flu. Hard but nice to be out. This is a short course but oddly pleasing. Smooth. Changing directions on the pine loop breaks it up nicely.
Morning Row - thanks for the guidance today, Glenn! And for letting me row as much as I did.
Lunch Run - nice run, nicer company
